Mission:
DX-002

Title:
Atlas Launcher Opens Studio

Goal:
npm run atlas must open Atlas Studio — not the regular app home screen.

Focus:
Default launch route /studio/ceo-workflow with /studio fallback
Prevent Expo from auto-opening browser to /
Launcher output: Atlas Studio ready · Opening CEO Workflow

Constraints:
npm start unchanged for normal app
Do not break Expo runtime startup
TypeScript clean

Success:
npm run atlas opens browser directly to Atlas Studio CEO Workflow.
